1.6.2.1.name: pmdumuid/kbw-countdown
1.6.2.1.description: This plugin sets a div or span to show a countdown to a given time. * Standard or compact formats, or create your own layout. * Decide which periods to show. * Count up from a date/time instead. * Cater for timezone differences and synchronise with server time. * Over 45 localisations.
